summary:
True hospitality consists of giving the best of yourself to your guests.
An open-minded and organized teamplayer who developed a passion for hospitality & gastronomy. Determined to learn and improve new skills every day. A stimulated perfectionist with a professional mindset who makes calculated decisions.
